{"tid":550901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊大宅被貼「下台」揮春","createTime":"2018-02-05T07:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T07:51:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"deef0443043d4dc9c8d271e297b0c153d943655a","tid":550901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:37:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180205/20295505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F20295505&d=lcuFvZK4NcesZK%2FZ6r0c4QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=bbc8aa71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F20295505&h=e3239171\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180205/20295505</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊大宅被貼「下台」揮春<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180205/large/05la2p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180205%2Flarge%2F05la2p8.jpg&h=94c9c6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭若驊被揭發僭建的屯門海詩別墅大閘昨被貼滿示威揮春。張志華攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】律政司司長鄭若驊被揭發屯門海詩別墅僭建，其位於南區的物業也有3處違規改動，人民力量成員「快必」譚得志昨率10多名人力成員到鄭若驊涉僭建的屯門大宅外抗議，指要與鄭「拜早年」，促其引咎下台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人力籲市民周日遊行<br />\n<br />\n多個持有物業有僭建的鄭若驊獲特首林鄭月娥幾度力撐，堅拒辭職，林鄭更呼籲社會「包容」鄭若驊，惹來各界反彈。譚得志昨率10多名人力成員到鄭若驊涉僭建的屯門海詩別墅與鄭「拜早年」，在大宅大閘外貼出多張寫上「僭建驊」和「下台」的揮春，促鄭若驊下台。<br />\n<br />\n譚得志期間在大宅外用咪大聲批評鄭的僭建行為無恥，表現較董建華更不濟，又向附近的居民指，該處樓價會因為鄭若驊起天台、掘地牢而急速跌價，「請你哋記住罪魁禍首係鄭若驊」，呼籲市民下周日參與遊行，向鄭表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n■記者廖梓霖"},{"pid":"2719d4ebf78380c08dfa2919cde77a79b75bdd59","tid":550901,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934810c23b024d46c2adcf9899bed355f3920925","tid":550901,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"算唔算係行為藝術"},{"pid":"d65d0f91355c3ce874f662f900ed5c8c45a365a5","tid":550901,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"一人千五 政府又肥肥了"},{"pid":"ec5abf68c9fa1d1fe614e663b665e52046b3c9f8","tid":550901,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:45:38.000Z","msg":"邊似揮春呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ec1bb51aca3362197a019714317387b2951f05","tid":550901,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"934810c23b024d46c2adcf9899bed355f3920925","tid":550901,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"算唔算係行為藝術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n齋睇張圖無睇內文<br />\n<br />\n見到人民力量呢四隻字 當我無問過"},{"pid":"f42c153f386ebe0f89bda9f23ccf0004afe39591","tid":550901,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"未入都知係邊個做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前689又係呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}